task.summary: Default task
Fully back click responsive now. Fixed small button colour logic issue with parts.
Queue portal now updates the database sign-off entries.
Improved formatting.
Updated to use Bootstrap 4.
Better styling for button readability.
Improved accessibility in the queue portal.
Improved readability of javascript - Moved HTML creation logic and renamed variables.
Refined button html generation logic.
Heavily reformatted naming conventions and string use in button generation logic.
Database checks now complete for log ins relating to year and module code supplied. Improved some naming conventions in the javascript for queue portal.
Improved navbar mobile responsive appearance
Fixed issues between manual sign-offs and queue use in the portal. Fixed memcached logic flaw when setting assigned demonstrators.
Added basic lecturer view modules functionality. Created initial create module interface for demonstrators. Functionality needs improvement.
Add module functionality complete currently without the assignment of users for that module.
Added file upload functionality to add users to a module during the module class creation process.
Added general export class functionality. Fixed small grouping logic.
Added libs for external styling and js code. Added delete and view demonstrators features to view module portal. Enforced lowercase for module creation.
Added ability for lecturers to edit the users in their registered modules.
Added logic to ensure sign-off requests are assigned, unassigned and also provided visual prompts to alert demonstrators and lecturers if there are waiting requests.
Added admin group that can view all modules.
Admins can now manage other admins.
Much improved login interface added.
Added enter key press events for ease of use.
Added new lecturer functionality. Fixed placeholder add new module start date.
Completed implementation refinements for worksheet locking. Also added checks to avoid worksheet lock bypassing and maximum percentage manipulation.
Refactored some queue portal code. Renamed logout button to mention changing module. Number of students waiting for sign off in a module now always mentioned. Formatted sign off confirmation dialog.
Hidden questions and parts from the sign-off portal if not relevant. Fixed issue with class creation (worksheet with parts only.)
Improved error checking for failed database queries. Fixed locked worksheet issue with improved queue portal changes.
Fixed uncaught fail echo
Fixed small no locked worksheets issue for sign-off completion. Improved error checking for memcached queries.
Added functionality to append results to a pre-existing gc document
Helped prevent students sending multiple requests for sign-off.
Added percentages and lock-date export.
Confirmation dialogs for user removal. Mobile friendly elements added (padding, wrapping). Improved text and formatting overall.
Removed redundant username reference in content of memcached values.
Small redundant code references deleted.
Enforced redirects in security.
Added jest testing for button generation
Restructured before any full manual testing.
Fixed sign off portal issue highlighted in Selenium testing.
Added Selenium file
Added Selenium instructions to readme
README now contains the installation instructions.
Mentioned readme edits for auth process.
Fixed small reload issue not clearing js script.
Comments added. Small edits to queue logic.
Referenced test files
Update to match dissertation submission. Date exploit fixes added.
Updated README to contain updated installation guide.
